le=\"color: red;\">成撚日幫細路申鼻涕 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n成撚日見佢地懶屎懶尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日係水腳毛都無一條 腳識反光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教人游水要拎 性罪行記錄 check 你做唔做得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解要幫？<br />\n班細路叫你做？</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n佢地有鼻涕唔識申 會換唔到氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n直接幫佢地申 用手 <br />\n申完放係池邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd93fba3d2c206b83d4fedd6ad2826196140cdde","tid":113554,"uid":40460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:34:04.000Z","msg":"有冇教囡囡？"},{"pid":"a17c2767be48b0d628928546f07654d8325fcc4a","tid":113554,"uid":58750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:36:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我成20歲人都唔識游水<br />\n一開始應該點學<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實大人學游水 最驚係心理關口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開波試下係水行下 <br />\n緊係唔好去大池 去訓練池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行完 有自信就 就去學換氣先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用口吹波波 吹5-6秒上黎 <br />\n用口吸氣"},{"pid":"a7895f5373190e2fa2fed9145b2ea92da8f253ed","tid":113554,"uid":5266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:36:37.000Z","msg":"咁除左暑假呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e20f65d412a822e1147861727a372116525629c","tid":113554,"uid":58750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:37:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收幾錢 想學</blockquote><br />\n 私人單對單 300 一個鐘 算低的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 睇地區"},{"pid":"fb241adc436561b2a08e3258f416cdcfd01e79a3","tid":113554,"uid":58750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:38:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇教囡囡？</blockquote><br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過好撚麻煩 通過中學女仔比番女miss教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b55d74b3cba6f82765fe418d667bdb298e5a4d","tid":113554,"uid":58750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:39:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁除左暑假呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一到 冬天 就收入減半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n你地冬天步都唔跑啦 游咩水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfabf03810c923d0a0dd6ebbfdcc73cb8713860","tid":113554,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:41:00.000Z","msg":"我諗住遲考救生員做ft 再考遊水教練做pt <br />\n聽人講遊水教練行業競爭大 係咪真架？"},{"pid":"329221a40802d690b264ad608d391e33b4ab103c","tid":113554,"uid":58750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:43:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗住遲考救生員做ft 再考遊水教練做pt <br />\n聽人講遊水教練行業競爭大 係咪真架？</blockquote><br />\n最好識人入行好點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔識人入行  屎記比緊40-60 一個鐘 <br />\n講緊有 銅章<br />\n有教練牌就 100 up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97cc4a38bcb280a7e9c23aead439fb8e4252e619","tid":113554,"uid":5266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T07:12:06.000Z","msg":"個牌咁撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742cc6cfc2be75d1d3ec2b85023c209a0db261b5","tid":113554,"uid":58750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:09:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個牌咁撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n6000 姐😂 會搵得番"},{"pid":"14066a6fa7b608389bc7ab5bba3d8960e4763f70","tid":113554,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:29:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>收幾錢 想學</blockquote><br />\n 私人單對單 300 一個鐘 算低的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 睇地區</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我十幾年前學游水一個鐘100<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616db0e39bf5bd1055498fb4813c35f070689e22","tid":113554,"uid":58750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:35:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>收幾錢 想學</blockquote><br />\n 私人單對單 300 一個鐘 算低的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 睇地區</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我十幾年前學游水一個鐘100<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 單對單咁教？"},{"pid":"6f32797c73e53423cbeca862774da2ddd5048b10","tid":113554,"uid":37736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:38:24.000Z","msg":"考泳總定教師會？<br />\n<br />\n你全私鐘？ 一個月搵到咁多"},{"pid":"22b93b6208c3196d32a23ff1e00a2ba71c08a6b9","tid":113554,"uid":5004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:41:56.000Z","msg":"個人浮唔起，有無咩秘訣/心得？"},{"pid":"157c680068471e8b26b26b77914433490dde9fc7","tid":113554,"uid":20557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T06:26:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個人浮唔起，有無咩秘訣/心得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n首先，你要明白以下幾點<br />\n1. 無空氣係體內係會沉。<br />\n2. 吸大啖氣會浮，不過個肺係上半身，所以腳係會沉。<br />\n3. 脂肪比高易浮，相反則易沉。男死屍多數面向水底，女死屍多數面向天，肥人死屍都係面向天多，都係同脂肪比有關。<br />\n4. 個人保持水平會浮，垂直會沉，呢個同重心有關<br />\n5. 放鬆會易d浮，緊張肌肉收緊晒會沉<br />\n<br />\n所以如果你指齋浮，做齊：<br />\n吸大啖氣，保持水平，放鬆，基本上會浮，最好做埋流線型動作<br />\n<br />\n但係如果你指要持續向前/後游，兼持續換氣，兼浮，有2個建議：<br />\n1. 明白以上原理，睇正確示範，係絕對安全兼水深唔過胸兼有救生員既泳池，自行學習<br />\n2. 正正經經揾個教練／成人班學啦"},{"pid":"8f97a9e6d3dab7df56b514eaf491966313206c55","tid":113554,"uid":49995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T07:01:25.000Z","msg":"黎緊七月會考牌<br />\n做過救生員<br />\n私池康記都番過<br />\n但係教水就冇經驗又唔識人<br />\n所以一拎到牌就去史記到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n如果想單對單教通常點搵客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa75a274b31c7ebff6ff55ff7e922e90bcbf4aa2","tid":113554,"uid":12653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T07:33:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊七月會考牌<br />\n做過救生員<br />\n私池康記都番過<br />\n但係教水就冇經驗又唔識人<br />\n所以一拎到牌就去史記到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n如果想單對單教通常點搵客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄你七月考牌，入得行都冬天啦喎<br />\n怕唔怕冇生意？"},{"pid":"f39407568f41f6658c804b5419c210b39c42fc79","tid":113554,"uid":20557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊七月會考牌<br />\n做過救生員<br />\n私池康記都番過<br />\n但係教水就冇經驗又唔識人<br />\n所以一拎到牌就去史記到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n如果想單對單教通常點搵客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄100M四式 如何？"},{"pid":"bbfb38545e5a179f36073068efd57c78000af77c","tid":113554,"uid":49995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:58:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黎緊七月會考牌<br />\n做過救生員<br />\n私池康記都番過<br />\n但係教水就冇經驗又唔識人<br />\n所以一拎到牌就去史記到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n如果想單對單教通常點搵客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄100M四式 如何？</blockquote><br />\n你講幾耐遊完?<br />\n好耐冇計過唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過以前有跟泳會練水<br />\n肯定正常時間內游到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dfc7893b74ea9ada8d953260f5ab5e25a1b86d5","tid":113554,"uid":49995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:59:13.000Z","ms